WEBVTT

00:02:57.590 --> 00:03:02.052
kwakuwa yeye na wanaharakati wengine
wanaunga mkono vyombo vya habari Kurdi.

00:03:03.025 --> 00:03:06.712
Hatua za kupinga ugaidi haraka
zinageuka kandamizi kwa taifa

00:03:06.736 --> 00:03:09.812
bila ulinzi madhubuti
kwa jamii ya walio wachache

00:03:10.297 --> 00:03:12.338
na kwa mdahalo wa amani;

00:03:13.675 --> 00:03:16.675
hii inahitaji kuungwa mkono na
chombo huru cha habari

00:03:17.749 --> 00:03:20.053
Lakini kwa kuwa hiyo haitokei,

00:03:20.077 --> 00:03:24.068
Washington inaungana na Silicon Valley
pamoja na Hollywood

00:03:24.701 --> 00:03:29.077
kuweka mamilioni-- mamia 
ya mamilioni ya dola

00:03:29.101 --> 00:03:31.688
katika kinachoitwa "kupinga - ujumbe"